ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.v23.datatype

Class CM_NDL

  • java.lang.Object
    • ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.AbstractType
      • ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.AbstractComposite
        • ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.v23.datatype.CM_NDL
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Composite, Type, Visitable, Serializable

    public class CM_NDL
extends AbstractComposite

    Represents an HL7 CM_NDL (observing practitioner) data type. This type consists of the following components:

    • OP name (CN)
    • start date/time (TS)
    • end date/time (TS)
    • point of care (IS) (IS)
    • room (IS)
    • bed (IS)
    • facility (HD) (HD)
    • location status (IS)
    • person location type (IS)
    • building (IS)
    • floor (ST)
